      1789
    ],
    "category": "Formula",
    "text": "$$\n\\text{A. } \\cos \\varphi = \\frac{aa' + bb' + cc'}{\\sqrt{a^2 + b^2 + c^2} \\cdot \\sqrt{a'^2 + b'^2 + c'^2}}.\n$$"
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      223,
