    "text": "$$\n\\text{C. } \\sin \\varphi = \\frac{|aa' + bb' + cc'|}{\\sqrt{a^2 + b^2 + c^2} \\cdot \\sqrt{a'^2 + b'^2 + c'^2}}.\n$$"
  },
  {
